        <td width="655" colspan="2">
          <h3><font size="4" face="Arial"><a name="husbandry"></a>Animal
        Husbandry</font></h3>
          <p><font face="Arial">Among the Baraïn
        of the Guéra and in the Dar Dadjo region, veterinary
        agents in Melfi take care of the health of the sheep,
        goats and cattle of the area.</font></p>
        </td>
        <td valign="top">&nbsp;</td>
    </tr>
